cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision applications, specifically on tracking superpixels over extended time periods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also heavily relies on unsupervised learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with video processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.RO (Robotics).
